cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation evaluation. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses BERT, a popular deep learning model, for the evaluation task. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as BERT is a neural network-based model. Finally, it could also be classified under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as BERT has been used for various computer vision tasks as well.
